            </div>

            <div class="row feedback">
                <h3 class="gap-top-xsmall">Give feedback</h3>
                <p>
                    Can we steal 2 minutes of your time to learn your opinion about this app?
                </p>
                <p>
                    <a href="//handsoncode.typeform.com/to/NeUbrn" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">
                        Fill out this quick survey
                    </a>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
